Fortis Healthcare Panel to Value International Operations

-- B y   K a r t h i k e y a n   S u n d a r a m
-- 
2011-09-19T07:56:14Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-19/fortis-healthcare-panel-to-value-international-operations.html
A panel at Fortis Healthcare India
Ltd., which agreed to acquire its international unit from RHC
Financial Services Ltd. today, will value the overseas business,
Managing Director Shivinder Mohan Singh said in  New Delhi  today.  The consolidation will be completed by December, he said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
